Insider Activity


Individual




Howard L. Carver



Mr. Howard L. Carver, CPA, is Independent Non-Executive Director at StoneMor Partners LP, Independent Non-Executive Director at StoneMor GP LLC, Independent Director at Assurant, Inc., a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, and a Member at The Connecticut Society of Certified Public Accountants. He is on the Board of Directors at Pinnacol Assurance, StoneMor Partners LP, StoneMor GP LLC, Assurant, Inc., University of Wisconsin, and Wadsworth Atheneum Museum of Art.
Mr. Carver was previously employed as Managing Partner by Ernst & Young LLP. He also served on the board at Open Solutions, Inc. and Phoenix National Trust Co.



